'''Rrann Hhoss''' was a gaming event in [[Togoria/Legends|Togoria]] centered in the use of [[sc'rath]] scimitars in combat and hunting.<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

Young hunter [[Mlatar Thon Gra]] won a Rran Hhoss when his tribe was invited to travel with the [[Margrave/Legends|Margrave's]] camp. When he won, he attracted the attention of smith [[Elotis]], who offered him a job as his apprentice.<ref name="AIR" />

